M|diana|- Never skip the QA gate — Quinn must sign off before shipping
M|diana|- Cross-vtr work that touches shared infrastructure (NavBar, layout, Supabase schema) must involve Dev for architectural ap
M|diana|- Operational bottlenecks: report to Marcus with data, not just observations
M|diana|- War Room max 2 specialists (enforced) — prevents dec paralysis
